Question:
Input:-			
	
Employee:-		
	emp_id	Name	Skills         
	1	       abc	spark,scala
	2	       pqr	hive
	3	       xyz	screening
	
Department:-		
	dept_id	dept_name emp_ids 
	abc1	      IT	   1,2
	abc2	      HR	   3

Output:-			
	dept_name	skills	
	IT	        spark, scala, hive	
	HR	        screening


Solution:
with cte as 
(select * from Dept cross apply string_split(emp_ids,',') x
join
EMPLOYEE e
on x.value=e.empId
)
select dept_name,string_agg(skills, ',') as skills_list from
cte group by dept_name
